1
00:00:40,100 --> 00:00:46,719
The last intersection still counts the hours
마지막 교차로는 아직도 시간을 헤아리네.

2
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:53,420
Red yellow green for empty towers
텅 빈 빌딩들을 위한 빨강 노랑 초록.

3
00:00:55,340 --> 00:01:00,280
Concrete veins where nothing flows
아무것도 흐르지 않는 콘크리트 혈관.

4
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:07,060
A faithful machine that never knows
결코 알지 못하는 충실한 기계.

5
00:01:07,060 --> 00:01:11,640
Still changing colors for no one there
아무도 없는데도 여전히 색을 바꾸네.

6
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:15,159
A signal thrown into the air
허공에 던져진 신호.

7
00:01:15,159 --> 00:01:18,799
No hand to stop no wheel to turn
멈출 손도, 돌릴 바퀴도 없어.

8
00:01:18,799 --> 00:01:22,540
It keeps on burning just to burn
그저 불타기 위해 계속 불타오르네.

9
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:42,319
The paint is peeling off the lanes
차선 위 페인트는 벗겨지고.

10
00:01:42,319 --> 00:01:45,799
The crosswalk faded by the rains
빗물에 바랜 횡단보도.

11
00:01:45,799 --> 00:01:49,120
But every thirty seconds sharp
하지만 정확히 30초마다.

12
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:54,700
It shifts its light like a beating heart
뛰는 심장처럼 불빛을 바꾸네.

